OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIn Mariupol, children bear 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthe brunt of Vladimir      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FPutin's war                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, In his hospital bed, little Artem      
OL,6, stares into space. He clutches a small 
OL,7, yellow toy tractor but says nothing as 
OL,8, specialist nurses monitor his          
OL,9, condition. The Russian shell that      
OL,10, blasted shrapnel into his belly also   
OL,11, badly wounded his parents and          
OL,12, grandparents as they tried to flee     
OL,13, Mariupol. A victim of Putin's war and  
OL,14, he's not yet three years old.          
OL,16,FIn the next bed to Artem lies          
OL,17,F15-year-old Masha, also from near      
OL,18,FMariupol. Her right leg was amputated  
OL,19,Fafter it was torn apart by the blast   
OL,20,Ffrom a Russian shell last Tuesday.     
